OVERVIEW: List files in the project or a specific group

USAGE: xcodeproj-cli list-files [--project <project>] [--workspace <workspace>] [--verbose] [--dry-run] [<group-name>] [--target <target>]

ARGUMENTS:
  <group-name>            Optional: specific group to list files from

OPTIONS:
  -p, --project <project> Path to .xcodeproj file (default: looks for
                          *.xcodeproj in current directory)
  -w, --workspace <workspace>
                          Path to .xcworkspace file
  -V, --verbose           Enable verbose output with performance metrics
  --dry-run               Preview changes without saving
  -t, --target <target>   Optional: list only files in specified target
  --version               Show the version.
  -h, --help              Show help information.

